</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[189,1398,1583,1645]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
<taxonomicName authorityName="H. J. Atkins &amp; Cronk (Atkins &amp; Cronk" authorityYear="2001" box="[189,423,1583,1609]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Cyrtandra" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hirtigera">
<emphasis box="[189,423,1583,1609]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Cyrtandra hirtigera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distributed throughout the island of 
<collectingRegion box="[879,978,1583,1609]" country="Philippines" name="Palawan" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Palawan</collectingRegion>
and is usually found on slopes near gullies at 
<quantity box="[303,422,1619,1645]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.65" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="0.3" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" unit="m" value="465.0" valueMax="900.0" valueMin="30.0">30–900 m</quantity>
a.s.l.
</paragraph>
